{"tid":2508885,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"伊朗快艇波斯灣逼近 美艦開火示警","createTime":"2021-04-29T05:38:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T05:38:57.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ab3c600c078df6a0b5c11b73def57c2aedee3be8","tid":2508885,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:38:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210429/2LWWRF4N55CMXPSLJ2BIAVCJ7M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210429%2F2LWWRF4N55CMXPSLJ2BIAVCJ7M%2F&d=DgCTbN7XbHZJJfbPUwNNzbPkHgDHOcRHwLuXI7BMvHI%3D&h=e03e07ae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210429%2F2LWWRF4N55CMXPSLJ2BIAVCJ7M%2F&h=1d7d8000\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210429/2LWWRF4N55CMXPSLJ2BIAVCJ7M/</a><br />\n<br />\n伊朗快艇波斯灣逼近 美艦開火示警<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/8VGHvyTAeY6f5e-B0XSLa-ZTNK0=/510x287/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/K4GNDUHAING5HPMNKGUOIMSEIY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F8VGHvyTAeY6f5e-B0XSLa-ZTNK0%3D%2F510x287%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FK4GNDUHAING5HPMNKGUOIMSEIY.jpg&h=49c7a5e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■美軍巡邏艦「霹靂號」。 美聯社<br />\n<br />\n美軍昨日指巡邏艦「霹靂號」周一在波斯灣執勤期間，遇到三艘伊朗革命衞隊快艇高速逼近至62米範圍內，結果「霹靂號」要開火示警。這是一個月內，美國第二度指摘伊朗騷擾區內美軍。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美伊核協議有眉目<br />\n<br />\n今個月初，一艘伊朗快艇突然切入美國海岸警衞隊巡邏艦「莫諾穆瓦號」的航線，導致後者急煞停，美軍批評伊方做法「危險且不專業」。<br />\n<br />\n伊朗革命衞隊不隸屬於伊軍，只聽命於最高精神領袖哈梅內伊，衞隊。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n由中、英、德、法、俄做中間人，拉攏美、伊的核協議似乎已有眉目，雙方已同意加快進度。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n另外，沙地阿拉伯王儲<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n路透社"}]}